Video-Xine version 0.02
=======================

This interface was developed as part of the Video::PlaybackMachine
project, and as a first pass contains only enough functionality to get
it running. It's known to work on i386 running Fedora Core 2 and 3, and
on x86_64 on FC4.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  xine-lib, available from http://xinehq.de

In addition, if you wish to actually display video, you probably want:

  X11::FullScreen

which provides a workable, if extremely simple, user interface.

